lead_paragraph: Cristian Maidana scored against his former team in the 95th minute and the Houston Dynamo beat the 10-man Philadelphia Union 1-0 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Maidana Scores in 95th to Give Dynamo 1-0 Win Over Union
